    <!-- About the Project -->
    <section id="about-project">
        <h2>About the Project</h2>
        <p>This project aims to develop an eco-friendly village using scientific principles from Biology, Chemistry, Physics, and Computer Science.</p>
        <p>Our project features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Biology:</strong> Aeroponics & Hydroponics systems for sustainable agriculture.</li>
            <li><strong>Chemistry:</strong> A water purification system for clean water supply.</li>
            <li><strong>Physics:</strong> Hydraulic jack bridge and renewable energy sources (solar and hydroelectric).</li>
            <li><strong>Computer Science:</strong> Smart village design, interactive website, and 3D models.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

